---
title: Sweet Soy Chicken & Asian Chilli Slaw with Sesame Kūmara Fries & Mayo
description: This chicken has layers upon layers of flavour, first being cooked in our staple sweet-soy seasoning, then being
tossed in sweet chilli! Sesame-crusted kūmara fries and a crunchy, zingy slaw act as the perfect side-kicks to this
superstar dish.

